,"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-02-05T13:43:06Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Sarah Homer","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/sarah-homer","withdrawn":false}],"role":[{"content_id":"f74e21e3-57ac-40be-819f-f0c86e01b6d2","details":{"body":"<p>The Director General, Corporate Transformation sets and leads the department’s workplace transformation and estates strategy, aligning this to business strategy and the wider Civil Service workforce plan. </p>\n\n<p>They also support the Permanent Secretary in their capacity as lead Accounting Officer on Synergy, the Shared Services Transformation Programme for <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr>, Ministry of Justice, Home Office and Defra: a substantial change programme, hosted and sponsored in <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr> on behalf of the 4 departments. </p>\n\n<p>The role is accountable for: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>Synergy Cluster – supporting delivery of this programme as DG sponsor </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Estates strategy </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Workplace Transformation Programme strategy and programme sponsor </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Government reform in <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr></p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{"ordered_parent_organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D10","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions","base_path":"/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions","content_id":"b548a09f-8b35-4104-89f4-f1a40bf3136d","details":{"acronym":"DWP","brand":"department-for-work-pensions","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a37dab1e5274a7908e35204/s960_dwp-caxton-house-logo-960.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/